### Description

Query the list of resource scopes that the current user is authorized to access (business, business set, tenant set, etc.) with pagination.

Results are sorted by a fixed rule: authorized scopes first, then favorited scopes, then favor time descending. By default only the first 10 records are returned to avoid fetching a large dataset at once. This API does not return permission-application related fields.

### Request Parameters

#### Query Parameters

| Field  | Type | Required | Description |
|--------|------|----------|-------------|
| offset | int  | No       | Pagination offset starting from 0; defaults to 0 if omitted; must be greater than or equal to 0 |
| length | int  | No       | Number of records per page; defaults to 10 if omitted; valid range is 1 to 200 |

### Request Example

- GET

```json
/api/v4/get_user_authorized_scopes?offset=0&length=10
```

