### Response Parameters

{% include '_generic_v4_response.md.j2' %}

#### data

| Field      | Type  | Always Present | Description |
|------------|-------|----------------|-------------|
| total      | long  | Yes            | Total number of authorized resource scopes before pagination |
| offset     | int   | Yes            | Pagination offset used in this query, starting from 0 |
| length     | int   | Yes            | Page size used in this query |
| scope_list | array | Yes            | List of authorized resource scopes; empty array when there is no data |

##### scope_list[] item

| Field         | Type    | Always Present | Description |
|---------------|---------|----------------|-------------|
| bk_scope_type | string  | Yes            | Resource scope type. Possible values: `biz` (business), `biz_set` (business set), `tenant_set` (tenant set) |
| bk_scope_id   | string  | Yes            | Resource scope ID corresponding to `bk_scope_type`, representing a business ID, business-set ID, or tenant-set ID |
| name          | string  | Yes            | Resource scope name |
| favor         | boolean | Yes            | Whether the scope is favorited. Possible values: `true` (favorited), `false` (not favorited) |
| favor_time    | string  | No             | Favor time in format `yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS`; omitted when not favorited |
| time_zone     | string  | No             | Time zone of the resource scope, for example `Asia/Shanghai` |
